==Significant depictions in popular culture==
* Grodno is one of the starting towns of Lithuania in the turn-based strategy game Medieval II: Total War: Kingdoms.
* Grodno is a location for one of the missions in the alternate history RTS &quot;Command and Conquer: Red Alert&quot;; Grodno was part of the Soviet Union and the Allied forces must work to rescue a special operative before her execution in a Soviet military base.

